title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (21): Learning From/For Knowledge Bases
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Relation Extraction w/ Neural Nets
* Learning Embeddings from Knowledge Bases

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-21-kb.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/P58GOj91nnA
Next Video: https://youtu.be/rOiXjukeHSw

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
